Put "about:config" in the address bar, set "toolkit.legacyUserProfileCustomizations.stylesheets" true
Open the profile folder. By putting "about:support" in the address bar, click "Open Folder" next to "Profile Folder"
Copy "userChrome.css" and "userContent.css" to "chrome" folder (create if not exist)
Put Firefox in Default Theme, Compact Density and disables Menu Bar and Bookmarks Toolbar
Restart Firefox
